data.description: If you are looking for a perfect like-new home with a very competitive and assumable interest rate, check this out! This 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom two-story home offers plenty of space for your growing family. With 2,653 square feet, loft area, large kitchen, granite countertops, large walk/in closet and an additional flex space downstairs for that 5th bedroom or office space, there's truly room for everyone. The fully fenced premier lot offers no rear neighbors, ensuring privacy and tranquility. Picture yourself enjoying quality time with your family in the backyard and hosting great dinner parties in the updated kitchen. Commuting to Tampa and Orlando is a breeze, thanks to the proximity to I-4 and the Polk Parkway. And that's not all! The community of Riverstone offers resort-style amenities for you to enjoy. Enjoy the resort-style amenities, community pool, relax in the cabana, or have fun at the playground. Stay active with the fitness station, and make sure your furry friends have their share of outdoor fun too, with the small and large dog park. Don't wait any longer! This home is ready for you and your family to create lasting memories. Come experience convenience, luxury, and community living at Riverstone in Lakeland. You deserve it!
